author: Mishaal Rahman
title: Viper4Android Updated to v2.5.0.5 with Nougat Support
text:
Viper4Android Updated to v2.5.0.5 with Nougat Support 
With Android adding new features in every reason, there are fewer and fewer reasons to root your device. Viper4Android is still one of the reasons many people root. The incredibly powerful and popular audio modification has been officially updated to version 2.5.0.5 recently to bring full support for Android Nougat devices.
